reviewText: I love this one I got it on September 20 2005 and I love all the episodes

5 Undersea Adventures

Ripped Pants (From Season 1):
Everybody laughs at Spongebob for ripping his pants

Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy (From Season 1):
Spongebob and Patrick discover their favorites superheroes live in a retirement home.

Karate Choppers (From Season 1):
Spongebob and Sandy become so obsessed with Karate.

Gary Takes a Bath (From Season 2):
It's gonna take Spongebob everything to make Gary take a bath.

Jellyfish Hunter (From Season 2):
Spongebob is hired to get Jellyfish for the Krusty Krab.
